OTS_TICKETS---------------------------------
- A perl script to grab data from traffic tickets
- inputted as text files, outputs data in CSV format. 
-
-USAGE: ots_tickets [OPTIONS] (fields|courts|summary) FILE FILE FILE...
-
-Modes---------------------
- Fields	will grab and output as much data as possible and output appropriate headers followed by all found data for all given files 
- 
- Courts	Outputs a list of court dates and number of tickets scheduled for that day for all given files
- 
- Summary 	Outputs a per-file summary for all given files

OPTIONS------------------------------

-o FILE 	Redirects output to the specivied file.

-v 		Enables verbose output which is sent to STDERR 

-h 		Prints a usage message

